&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;This position is not eligible for relocation assistance. Visit our&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.pinterestcareers.com/pinflex/&quot;&gt;PinFlex&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;page to learn more about our working model.&lt;/li&gt;
