&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;This position is not eligible for relocation assistance. Visit our &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.pinterestcareers.com/pinflex/&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;PinFlex&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt; page to learn more about our working model.&lt;/li&gt;
